- Install service com.dome.home.vault-43ba0b40 if missing
- Start service com.dome.home.vault-43ba0b40

Optional after setup:
- Optionally connect calendar or Slack sources after setup.
- Optionally configure a local model provider after setup.

Warnings:
- Review the proposed Markdown scope before applying setup to existing owner content.

No changes were made."
